import { Tab, Tabs, TabList, TabPanel } from 'react-tabs'; import 'react-tabs/style/react-tabs.css'; import Headings from './Headings'; export default ({ resumedata }) => { console.log(resumedata, 'resumedata'); return ( <>
{resumedata.map((data, index) => ( {data.maincontent[0]?.heading || `Section ${index + 1}`} ))} {resumedata.map((data, index) => ( {data.maincontent.map((section, sectionIndex) => (
{section.resumeinfo ? (
{section.year}

{section.heading}

{section.resumeinfo.map((item, itemIndex) => (

{item.title}

{item.university}
{item.rating}

{item.content}

))}
) : section.professionalskills ? (
{section.year}

{section.heading}

{section.professionalskills.map((skill, skillIndex) => (

{skill.title}

{skill.subtitle}
{skill.skillsinfo.map((skillItem, skillItemIndex) => (
{skillItem.content}
{skillItem.rating}
))}
))}
) : (
No content available
)}
))} ))}
); };
